doc.knownrelatives: Zeus (father), Leto (mother); Apollo (brother), Gaea (great-grandmother), Ouranos (great-grandfather, deceased), Cronus, Rhea (paternal grandparents); Coeus, Phoebe (maternal grandparents), Ares, Dionysus, Hephaestus, Hercules, Hermes (half-brothers), Aphrodite, Eilithyia, Eris/Discord, Hebe, Persephone (half-sisters), Chiron, Hades, Poseidon (uncles), Asteria, Demeter, Hera, Vesta (aunts), Alex Aaron, Aristaeus, Cupid, Hermaphroditus (nephews), Aeneas, Asclepius, Troilius (nephews, deceased), Harmonia (niece)
doc.powers: Artemis possesses the average strength of a god allowing her to lift/press 30 tons and possessing extreme resistance to injury. She is also an immortal and in so being is long lived.
